item.title: Rinker 342 Express Cruiser
item.dc:creator: carspot-demodata
item.content:encoded:
SPIRIT 28 zählt zu den "modern classics".
Gutmütiges Regatta- und Familienboot, stabiles Seeschiff
Sloop getakelt, Gro 14,05 m², Rollfock Harken/Genua II 20,38 m², Blister 
ca. 38 m²
Eigner-gepflegt, aus Ersthand; Verkauf aus Altersgründen
Technik-Wartung durch Werft
Winterlager = Halle, Sommer = Stegplatz

  1. _ Kugel-Kompass, Echolot, Sumlog, *keine* 
  2. Bordelektronik
  3. 2 x Ankerleine je 30 m + 5 m Ketten-Vorlauf; 1 Pflugschar- + 1 
  4. Stock-Anker je 12,- kg
  5. Deck- und Rumpfausstattung: Bug- und Heckkorb Nirostahl; Relingstützen + 
  6. Badeleiter Niro
  7. Sprayhood und Relingskleid sind sandfarben
  8. 4 Lewmar-Winschen, Whale-Henderson Bilge-Pumpe
  9. Schleppanker/Kugel- und Ball-Signal, Radar-Refklektor
  10. _Zusätzl. Ausrüstung:_ Schleppleine 50 m, div. Leinen; Kleinmaterial + 
  11. Werkzeug.

This boat has the upgrade engines, the Mercruiser 6.0 Brovos.  She has AIR and HEAT , plus GENNY and a WINDLASS.  A perfect large cruiser without the large price.  Call for showing.

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: 65-71 Hester St, New York, NY 10002, USA

Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!
